      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit. This high-revving naturally aspirated inline-six benefits from recent VANOS servicing and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for maintaining chassis rigidity and long-term durability. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, transferring torque through a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Suspension kinematics are sharpened via upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver-focused example, the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory specification, and the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synchronized for immediate, linear throttle response. A purist\u2019s specification optimized for technical performance.",
